text: Bashkirskaya Urginka () is a rural locality (a village) in Novopetrovsky Selsoviet, Zianchurinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 866 as of 2010. There are 9 streets. == Geography == It is located 12 km from Isyangulovo, 9 km from Novopetrovskoye. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zianchurinsky District
title: Bashkirskaya Urginka
